Title: Educating Finch
Plot: Trying to find a photo for a show, Elliott chooses a nude photo of Maya he took when they were dating and she passed out drunk.  Jack hires a tutor for Finch, although she turns out to be a massage therapist as well.  When Finch confesses he got a massage instead of being tutored, Jack is happy because Finch is maturing.
GuestStars: Brigid Brannagh, Greg Proops, Edward James Gage
